7127,"uid":104138,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:35:17.000Z","msg":"有無報館或組織可以代為收帛金比佢屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a2a98fae1e394cea74c5ed143c0891469ead26c","tid":1227127,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:38:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a3aace92fb0c0db03652efb5c8ddc216c2502fa","tid":1227127,"uid":109629,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:41:12.000Z","msg":"推到有銀行acct為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nRIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86d434b20e8ed6dcefe70ce5dd9ff4227afb7eb4","tid":1227127,"uid":123050,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:41:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>行政機關濫用權力之審判</strong></span><br />\n二戰末期，納粹德國敗局已現，佛斯曼醫師、門格勒、拉舍爾三人的命運也隨著戰爭快速流轉。1945年時，拉舍爾因犯罪而被處死，和被他殺死的許多人一樣，葬身於達豪集中營裡。而門格勒假扮成一般士兵，躲過追緝後流亡到南美洲，直到1979年在巴西意外溺斃後才被確認身分。而始終堅持人性的佛斯曼醫師則在戰火中存活了下來，1945年時游過易北河後向美軍投降，戰後以泌尿科醫師的身份默默地生活著。在惡魔的年代結束之際，三名醫師分別擁來了他們各自的結局&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/5bd929a85b8a970c9c8fd7567b295223-e1450778342448.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpansci.asia%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F12%2F5bd929a85b8a970c9c8fd7567b295223-e1450778342448.jpg&h=327c7f1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n左上圖：將人浸入冰水當中，藉此研究在低溫下人體的反應；左下圖：故意讓小孩感染結核菌，並切除腋下的淋巴腺，測試人體的免疫力；右圖：紐倫堡審判中，對卡爾&middot;勃蘭特（Karl Brandt）醫師的審判，他被控同意並參與非人道實驗和其他戰爭罪行，最後被判絞刑。<br />\n用屍體換來的規範－紐倫堡守則<br />\n堆積如山的屍體、骨瘦如柴的幸存者，那些泯滅人性的實驗震撼了全世界。1948年在紐倫堡進行的醫師審判，被告的醫師之中，不乏知名的科學家，如施靈（Klaus Karl Schilling）曾是國際瘧疾研究聯盟的成員，戰時卻刻意讓一千多名囚犯感染瘧疾來進行科學研究。科學家在戰爭期間荒唐的行徑，讓美國醫師里昂&middot;亞歷山大（Leo Alexander）動筆起草人體實驗中應有的道德規範，也就是今日我們熟知的「紐倫堡公約」，寫明了醫師在任何情況之下，都不得傷害受試者（除非受試者就是醫師本人）。而1964年在芬蘭舉辦的全球醫師大會更提出「赫爾辛基宣言（The Declaration of Helsinki）」，說明了受試者有絕對的權利了解實驗內容，保障了受試者「知情同意」的權益。數十年的努力之下，美國和其他國家都誓言杜絕非人道的臨床實驗，全世界都認為這種惡魔般的人體實驗不會再出現了&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qp60jU2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqp60jU2.png&h=0f218e09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/62254048_1233250940184671_5825174709460795392_n.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-2.fna&amp;oh=af8a127ef43e169c16b9bc1668a17909&amp;oe=5D8A89DA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F62254048_1233250940184671_5825174709460795392_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-2.fna%26oh%3Daf8a127ef43e169c16b9bc1668a17909%26oe%3D5D8A89DA&h=582c6bc5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"40f29ad31dd47287405db417cbef3454b9a15f9e","tid":1227127,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:43:16.000Z","msg":"會"},{"pid":"574ac77508a1d0e7437d03bf71f3e45862cf45f1","tid":1227127,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:48:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc901f40372c4efe8dc3b74d2cdcc4bb0d203f08","tid":1227127,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a3aace92fb0c0db03652efb5c8ddc216c2502fa","tid":1227127,"uid":109629,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:41:12.000Z","msg":"推到有銀行acct為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br